&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Shires Health Care&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Are you an experienced pharmacist seeking new challenges? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for a self-motivated and enthusiastic registered pharmacist to join our friendly clinical team of 11 Doctors,  3 GP Registrars, 2 Nurse Practitioners, 2 Triage Nurse, Community Matron, Care Home Nurse 6 practice nurses and 2 pharmacy technicians.  The practice has a wide and well established team with passion for delivering quality patient care and experience in training.  We are looking for someone to join our expanding multi-disciplinary practice team.  This is an exciting challenge for someone who is highly motivated and keen to develop their clinical and professional skills. The post will suit an enthusiastic, experienced pharmacist.  We would prefer a prescribing pharmacist but the practice would be willing to train the successful applicant. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you are interested in the post please contact us to arrange an informal chat. We would love to hear from you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
